<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LearnWell Tuition Centre</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #333;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        nav a {
            float: left;
            display: block;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
            color: black;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .section {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>LearnWell Tuition Centre</h1>
        <p>Keeping the community informed and managing tuition services efficiently</p>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="#announcements">Announcements</a>
        <a href="#course-offerings">Course Offerings</a>
        <a href="#online-registration">Online Registration</a>
        <a href="#maintenance-requests">Maintenance Requests</a>
        <a href="#about-us">About Us</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        <section id="announcements" class="section">
            <h2>Announcements</h2>
            <p>Updates on class schedules, special events, and important notices will be posted here.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="course-offerings" class="section">
            <h2>Course Offerings</h2>
            <p>Details about available subjects, schedules, and fees will be listed here.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="online-registration" class="section">
            <h2>Online Registration</h2>
            <p>Enroll in classes and manage student profiles here.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="maintenance-requests" class="section">
            <h2>Maintenance Requests</h2>
            <p>Report issues or request assistance here.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="about-us" class="section">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Learn about our mission and teaching staff here.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="contact" class="section">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>Get in touch with us for inquiries and support here.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
